column1: TYRain_1677-1886_A_pt1-page-130.csv, TYRain_1677-1886_B_pt2-page-014.csv & TYRain_1677-1886_B_pt2-page-015.csv are essentially duplicates of each other with several efforts to correct possible mistranscriptions of original publications.

1810 - TYRain_1677-1886_B_pt2-page-113.csv provides, in the column intended for 1814, a 1975 transcription from the Gentleman Magazine of 1810, which demonstrates the months had been offset and December missed.
